{"tid":2026405,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女記者公廁遭警膝壓頸失禁","createTime":"2020-05-21T02:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T06:52:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"23552c54408ab3175296fe426489ae1db359998b","tid":2026405,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T02:38:10.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200521/62VCAJ2ESNTILN62VMYRMUCVKM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200521%2F62VCAJ2ESNTILN62VMYRMUCVKM%2F&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsT%2BQayrLlxBj8%2BPX1Ib8Zww%3D&h=cd68196b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200521%2F62VCAJ2ESNTILN62VMYRMUCVKM%2F&h=973d0b41\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200521/62VCAJ2ESNTILN62VMYRMUCVKM/</a><br />\n<br />\n女記者公廁遭警膝壓頸失禁<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警暴問題日趨嚴重，記者亦不能倖免。有女記者控訴本月10日母親節當晚，在旺角洗衣街公園採訪期間，被防暴警噴胡椒噴霧，並將她按在地上及用膝蓋跪向頸側及用腳踢背部，令她失去意識及失禁。有立法會議員批評警方施行酷刑，屬嚴重人道罪行。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：遇襲《蘋果》攝記擬聯同行家索償<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200521/large/1589995089_9cc6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200521%2Flarge%2F1589995089_9cc6.gif&h=4de5e198&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女記者被警員鎖上手銬送院，頭部有傷痕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n不斷向其面部、鼻及耳朵噴射胡椒噴霧，又叫她「黑記」、「曱甴」，其後四至五名警員將她按在地上，用膝蓋跪向其頸側、用腳踢背、用棍打頭，令她呼吸困難。她失去意識前，聽到有人問「有冇多支？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200521/large/1589995088_0f7b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200521%2Flarge%2F1589995088_0f7b.gif&h=f3c5209a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「娛賓」女記者當晚在公廁拍攝到防暴警用索帶綁上兩名少女的手。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兜頭淋水逼講「多謝」<br />\n<br />\n女記者醒來後發現雙手被綁及失禁，向警員要求水時，一名女警竟用水「兜頭淋」，並要她不斷講「多謝」，更有一把風扇吹向她，警員聲稱「幫你降溫」，令她十分寒冷。她送院時頭部有腫脹，手背及頭部至今仍感痛楚，拇指能動但不能用力。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n他在警署目睹有大批被捕男子擠在一個狹窄空間，警方又以有人打錯電話「玩嘢」，不准其他人打電話，剝奪被捕人士求助權利。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員尹兆堅形容<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n全面整肅警隊。<br />\n<br />\n警方稱<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n可向投訴警察課投訴。<br />\n<br />\n■記者何家朗"},{"pid":"86d147ebcfd800b44f42d46703466d3667aa8581","tid":2026405,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T02:38:35.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"d0c248bf7e4a18eb96c4e2ff12f87a0028fbc9f5","tid":2026405,"uid":56875,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T02:39:07.000Z","msg":"玩到失禁"},{"pid":"e644e330d3d10fe8992ff5d3a1eb2dd697c44c32","tid":2026405,"uid":68084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T02:39:47.000Z","msg":"好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1acfdb4cd57dee636324d819ab7f2854bb1fed3e","tid":2026405,"uid":6562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T02:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240de3bf2eec0388fb6a8d62e5e3574a515eeef9","tid":2026405,"uid":292497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d0c248bf7e4a18eb96c4e2ff12f87a0028fbc9f5","tid":2026405,"uid":56875,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T02:39:07.000Z","msg":"玩到失禁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T02:40:00.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啦食屎狗"},{"pid":"f4ac850021f79e29ec3093c3d1c6ae311b7d79b0","tid":2026405,"uid":358677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T02:40:10.000Z","msg":"痴撚晒線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963abd3f1874ef26f927ec4192caf1169bdfe243","tid":2026405,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T02:40:25.000Z","msg":"3樓 4樓"},{"pid":"038f469c768cf67b146725d60ff0f69a6708f08a","tid":2026405,"uid":234357,"like":0,"d